{"tid":2463402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Dominion投票系統告霍士新聞索償16億美元","createTime":"2021-03-26T16:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T16:26:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53936909bf3808616da06f57a36065f6674d6a35","tid":2463402,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選結果雖已塵埃落定，但相關訴訟仍在進行中。負責投票系統的Dominion與Smartmatic各自向福斯新聞索賠16億和27億美元，合計約合台幣1230億元，理由是福斯新聞和福斯商業新聞頻道在大選後的節目中，主持人和來賓頻頻指控投票系統不靠譜，有舞弊嫌疑，嚴重傷害商譽。<br />\n<br />\n福斯拒絕指控，表示以節目內容為榮，還說相關言論受到憲法第一增修條文的保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5346851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F5346851&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=ac8960d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5346851</a>"},{"pid":"0d24a45f90e97c06992e418be8a4b625db51febd","tid":2463402,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"講事實無問題"},{"pid":"e5591027c86e9c7dd10ce8aaada087bc228173d9","tid":2463402,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW1v8ibi2XYoZeHn837KUXig7ChrHVkjC2puU7VVWik9P?filename=PMicsGg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMicsGg.jpg&h=897ad1c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2f1ce94c3b02ee272918145fb44d797cb659e7b","tid":2463402,"uid":197563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"Dominion Cheating System<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdtUnKYCYERjivxZw9C2X18QxSriU8NbwPRwy1m1MSWLu?filename=psgdWDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsgdWDm.jpg&h=97700dba&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}